					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I think what you're supposed to do is take the voltage difference between $0F and $20 to represent only 0% to 75% or 80% luma (in sRGB, #000000 to #BFBFBF or #CCCCCC). That'll darken the overall picture but give headroom for over-bright colors.</div>

